Call Centre Agent
-
Date Posted: 2014/05/04 06:48:36
Ref. JB3046920
Job Description
Receive calls from clients and schedule appointments for mobile and in-store grooming services following strict company policy.
Answer inquiries and questions from clients regarding their pets and handle complaints.
Input all relevant client and appointment data into Animal Care's specialised software and update all relevant call sheets in excel.
This position will report directly to the Grooming Operations Coordinator.
Skills
Applicant needs to a have firm knowledge of spoken English and Arabic and easily understandable
Applicant must have strong people skills with a customer service focus.
Applicant must be able to conversely comfortably and professionally on the phone with good listening skills.
Applicant much be able to multi-task and have strong computer skills including but no limited to using search tools, browsers and also email features; attaching files to correspondence, utilizing tracking and management software and data entry.
